OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start to the morning
OL,6,Fwith a few spots of rain likely,
OL,7,Fbefore clearing eastwards into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Skies brightening by the
OL,9,Flate afternoon, into the evening, with
OL,10,Fplenty of sunshine developing.
OL,11,FGenerally feeling fresher than of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClearer skies for many
OL,14,Fovernight which will allow
OL,15,Ftemperatures to fall, giving a much
OL,16,Fmore comfortable night for many.
OL,17,FStaying dry with high cloud moving in
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
